================================
Classification Rules Recap
ONLY vowels → vowels.txt
Pattern: ^[aeiou]+$

ONLY consonants → consonants.txt
Pattern: ^[bcdfghjklmnpqrstvwxyz]+$
Mixed (starts with consonant, contains both) → mixed.txt
Conditions:

starts with consonant
contains at least one vowel
contains at least one consonant
Word-by-word evaluation



Word	Contains vowels	Contains consonants	Starts with consonant	Category
apple	yes	yes	no (starts with vowel)	—
orange	yes	yes	no	—
sky	no (y not counted)	yes	yes	consonants.txt
rhythm	no (y not counted)	yes	yes	consonants.txt
queue	yes	yes	no	—
fly	no (y not counted)	yes	yes	consonants.txt
echo	yes	yes	no	—
crypt	no (y not counted)	yes	yes	consonants.txt
